messages.message: I can't tell you how your message taught me a sweet lesson! In this age of high tech, I'm trying to get back to my mission in "high touch", and your simple message proved the intrinsic value in gratitude and simplicity!
I appreciate that, let me know if I can help further or if you have a need for an enthusiastic technologist. ;)
I will! I am a new venture out of CO+HOOTS Level Up! pilot, and I'm getting ready to launch.
What is cohoots, I've seen that on a few profiles I have come across.
It's a co-working space in Midtown.
